{{Han etym}}
From an ancient variant form of {{zh-l|*烏}}. Not related to {{zh-l|*方}} or {{zh-l|*㫃}}.

Note the other uses of {{zh-l|于}}, the simplified and variant traditional form of the preposition senses.

; Preposition
: From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*ʔaj||to go; directional particle}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). It has slowly merged with and replaced the older {{och-l|于}} ([[ibid.]]).
; Prefix in {{zh-l|*於菟/於檡/於兔/於䖘}}
: Variant of {{och-l|阿|prefix in kinship terms and personal names}} ([[ibid.]]).
